Bernard Lucking Zuroff

Linked companies :  Caesars Entertainment Corp 





Summary 



Mr. Bernard L. Zuroff is on the Board of Directors at Caesars Entertainment Corp. Mr. Zuroff was previously employed as Secretary & General Counsel by ICG Communications, Inc. and General Counsel by McLeod USA, Inc.



