Bernard L. Zuroff: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 24, 2017 6:44 PM ET
Diversified Telecommunication Services

Company Overview of McLeodUSA, LLC



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Bernard L. Zuroff  Group Vice President, Secretary, and General Counsel, McLeodUSA, LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships61--
Background

		Mr. Bernard L. Zuroff serves as Consultant and Associate of Vertical Partners. Mr. Zuroff served as Group Vice President, Secretary and General Counsel at McLeodUSA, LLC. from August 2006 to February 2008. From October 2004 to August 2006, he served as an Independent Consultant in the telecommunications industry. He served as General Counsel, Executive Vice President and Secretary of ICG Communications Inc. from October 2000 to October 2004. Prior to this position, Mr. ... Zuroff served as Assistant General Counsel and Corporate Attorney of ICG Communications Inc. from July 1996. Before joining ICG Communications Inc., he had eleven years of experience as an Attorney with Gorsuch Kirgis, L.L.C., the Resolution Trust Company and Infotel, Inc. He has practiced law for over twenty-three years in both private practice and as corporate in-house counsel. He has over nine years of experience in the telecommunications industry. Mr. Zuroff has been an Independent Director of Caesars Entertainment Corporation since November 10, 2016. He served as Director of Fisker Automotive, Inc. from November 2012 to November 2014. He served on Board of Trustees of InnKeepersUSA, Inc. from July 2010 to October 2011. Mr. Zuroff has a Bachelor of Arts degree in Accounting from Carroll College, a Juris Doctorate from the University of Montana and an LLM. in Taxation Law from New York University.Read Full Background




Corporate Headquarters
One Marthas WayHiawatha, Iowa 52233United StatesPhone: 319-790-7800Fax: 319-790-7767
